ISLAMABAD, Jun 16 (APP): Minister for Interior Rana Sanaullah on Thursday prayed for speedy recovery of Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz leader Daniyal Aziz, who sustained injuries in a traffic accident.
The minister also expressed deep grief over demise of another person in the accident, a press release said.
